{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/buka-bersama-ciayo-corp-silaturahmi-komikus-indonesia/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Buka Bersama CIAYO Corp, Menjalin Silaturahmi Dengan Komikus Indonesia","content":"<p>Pada hari Rabu, tanggal 7 Juni lalu, diadakan acara buka bersama CIAYO Corp. Acara yang diadakan di kantor CIAYO Corp. di kawasan Mangga Dua, Jakarta ini bertujuan sebagai sarana untuk menjalin silaturahmi serta bentuk hiburan menjelang hari raya Idul Fitri.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_48070\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-48070\" data-attachment-id=\"48070\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/buka-bersama-ciayo-corp-silaturahmi-komikus-indonesia/attachment/01-buka-bersama-ciayo-corp/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/01-buka-bersama-ciayo-corp.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"01-buka-bersama-ciayo-corp\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/01-buka-bersama-ciayo-corp-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/01-buka-bersama-ciayo-corp.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-48070\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/01-buka-bersama-ciayo-corp.jpg\" alt=\"buka bersama ciayo corp\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/01-buka-bersama-ciayo-corp.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/01-buka-bersama-ciayo-corp-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-48070\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Pictures</p></div></p>\n<p>Acara buka bersama dihadiri oleh segenap staf CIAYO Comics, CIAYO Games, CIAYO Blog, serta para komikus dan pelaku industri komik Indonesia. Beberapa komikus yang hadir di antaranya adalah komikus <a href=\"https://www.ciayo.com/id/comic/si-juki-mang-awung\">Si Juki</a> dan <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/asosiasi-komik-indonesia-aksi-deklarasi/\">ketua AKSI</a> <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/chit-chat/know-judges-2-faza-meonk/\">Faza Meonk</a>, komikus Komik Faktap dan <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/pakdhe-geng-bhinneka-problematika-indonesia-yang-dikemas-dengan-santai/\">Pakdhe &amp;</a> <a href=\"https://www.ciayo.com/id/comic/pakdhe-geng-bhinneka\">Geng Bhinneka</a> Iskandar Salim, sekjen AKSI <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/chit-chat/know-your-judges-6-imansyah-lubis/\">Imansyah Lubis</a>, komikus <a href=\"https://www.ciayo.com/id/comic/komikman-an-ordinary-family-life\">Komikman</a> <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/chit-chat/komikman-pengisi-waktu-luang-yang-sekarang-terkenal/\">Dirga Deka</a>, komikus <a href=\"https://www.ciayo.com/id/comic/wavelength\">Wavelength</a> Shikacchi, dan masih banyak lagi. Selain itu, ada juga perwakilan media dari Duniaku serta Wikipedia Indonesia.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_48071\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-48071\" data-attachment-id=\"48071\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/buka-bersama-ciayo-corp-silaturahmi-komikus-indonesia/attachment/02-buka-bersama-ciayo-corp/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/02-buka-bersama-ciayo-corp.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02-buka-bersama-ciayo-corp\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/02-buka-bersama-ciayo-corp-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/02-buka-bersama-ciayo-corp.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-48071\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/02-buka-bersama-ciayo-corp.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: CIAYO Pictures\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/02-buka-bersama-ciayo-corp.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/02-buka-bersama-ciayo-corp-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-48071\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Pictures</p></div></p>\n<p>Acara berlangsung sederhana dan cukup singkat, dengan pembukaan dari CEO CIAYO Corp. Borton Liew. Dalam sambutannya, Borton mengingatkan tentang pentingnya keseimbangan antara karir dan ibadah, terutama dalam momen Ramadhan. Mewakili segenap CIAYO Corp., Borton juga mengucapkan permohonan maaf lahir dan batin.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_48072\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-48072\" data-attachment-id=\"48072\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/buka-bersama-ciayo-corp-silaturahmi-komikus-indonesia/attachment/03-buka-bersama-ciayo-corp/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/03-buka-bersama-ciayo-corp.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03-buka-bersama-ciayo-corp\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/03-buka-bersama-ciayo-corp-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/03-buka-bersama-ciayo-corp.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-48072\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/03-buka-bersama-ciayo-corp.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: CIAYO Pictures\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/03-buka-bersama-ciayo-corp.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/03-buka-bersama-ciayo-corp-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-48072\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Pictures</p></div></p>\n<p>Karena momen acara hanya berjarak beberapa menit saja sebelum berbuka, para staf CIAYO Corp. serta undangan langsung dipersilakan untuk menyantap sajian berbuka begitu adzan maghrib berkumandang. Semua undangan mendapatkan suguhan makanan lezat .</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_48074\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-48074\" data-attachment-id=\"48074\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/buka-bersama-ciayo-corp-silaturahmi-komikus-indonesia/attachment/05-buka-bersama-ciayo-corp/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/05-buka-bersama-ciayo-corp.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"05-buka-bersama-ciayo-corp\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/05-buka-bersama-ciayo-corp-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/05-buka-bersama-ciayo-corp.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-48074\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/05-buka-bersama-ciayo-corp.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: CIAYO Pictures\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/05-buka-bersama-ciayo-corp.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/05-buka-bersama-ciayo-corp-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-48074\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Pictures</p></div></p>\n<p>Kamu ingin jadi bagian dari keseruan CIAYO Corp.? Momennya pas banget, karena CIAYO Corp. butuh kemampuan kamu yang jago di bidang sosial media dan desain grafis. Kirimkan CV dan portfolio kekinian kamu ke <a href=\"mailto:join@ciayo.com\">join@ciayo.com</a> kalau kamu merasa posisi ini cocok buat kamu. Untuk informasi lebih lanjut, klik <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/permalink.php?story_fbid=10214211019782255&amp;id=1617482934\">di sini</a>.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_48077\" 